OL,3,CBus passengers hit by 'costly start to
OL,4,C2025' after 50% rise in fares
OL,6,FMillions of bus passengers in England
OL,7,Fhave been hit by an increase in single
OL,8,Ffares from #2 to #3.
OL,10,FThe Government increased the bus fare
OL,11,Fcap on Wednesday for the first time
OL,12,Fsince it was launched for most routes
OL,13,Ftwo years ago.
OL,15,FIt will remain at #3 until the end of
OL,16,F2025.
OL,18,FThe Department for Transport (DfT)
OL,19,Fsaid this will enable "potential
OL,20,Fsavings of up to 80% on some routes".
