OL,6,F"The fare cap has proved popular with
OL,7,Fpassengers and helped boost ridership,
OL,8,Fso the Government must now look for a
OL,9,Flong-term replacement for the scheme
OL,10,Ffrom next year to avoid any further
OL,11,Frises."
