OL,14,Fannounced in Chancellor Rachel Reeves'
OL,15,Ffirst Budget in October 2024, a
OL,16,FGovernment source said maintaining an
OL,17,Fupper limit for bus fares was "hard
OL,18,Ffought for in the Budget process" and
OL,19,Fis largely aimed at helping passengers
OL,20,Fin rural areas.
